Registration has closed for all events, but I wanted a to provide a place where TMIRCE members could post that they will be attending and which event they'll be doing. The Most Informal Relay Team Ever will consist of Christina, Erin, Sean, and myself, so if you're running the half and can stand to go back outside and cheer, I'll be running the final leg.
